    BinaryHeapA creates a minimum BinaryHeap. Values can be inserted or deleted, and the heap will rebalance itself from the methods heapify, moveUp, and moveDown. moveUp and moveDown move lesser values up the tree and greater values down the tree, respectively. The user can also get the value of any cell in the vector.
